{
  "stem": "54.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Much, much worse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because my father was very hungry all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to give him our piece of bread-- what I had for myself, I give it to him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because he was so hungry, that one day he decided that he was going to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, when we were in Lodz, they called him from Kripo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was a police station where, if somebody went in there, he didn't end a life, his life was already finished.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But unfortunate, when they took him the first time there, they took his fingers, and they put in the door-- they opened the door, they put the fingers in the door, and they locked-- they closed the door.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You can imagine how he came home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His nails were up here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was very sick that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But what we could, we did for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he never recuperate from this because his nail were up already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "All his nails fall out his fingers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we did whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We shared our little food, what we got for us, we shared with our parents because my father was so hungry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And one day they came and they called him again to Kripo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "After a while, they called him again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the morning before we got up, all of us, we didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got dressed and he throw himself down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he said he was not able to go again to Kripo and to be there for so long, so many days, and to go through the torture what he went through.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this we had to thank a woman from our city.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
